review_text: The park itself is nice, but the bathrooms aren't maintained. There was poop in front of the door that hadn't been cleaned and the smell was awful

(Translated by Google) I recently went with my daughter and it was fun. However, winter is not recommended, given the ice and snow (risk of injury). Otherwise, in summer the swimming pool is very accessible for all.

(Original)
J'y suis allée récemment avec ma fille et c'était sympa. Par contre, l'hiver ce n'est pas recommandé, étant donné la glace et la neige (risque de blessures). Sinon, l'été la piscine est très accessible pour tous.
